descriptionOfWork: Repair and replace damaged roof tiles.
Replace all windows with energy-efficient ones.
Full renovation of the kitchen area.
Replace the old heating system with a new one.
Complete overhaul of the main bathroom.
Paint the exterior walls and fences.
Fix leaks and replace pipes in the kitchen and bathroom.
Install solar panels on the roof.
Renovate the garden and add new plants.
Redesign the interior with new furniture and decor.
Install a new electricity meter for accurate billing.
Repair and repaint window frames.
Install a new automated garage door.
Install insulation in the attic for better energy efficiency.
Repave the driveway with new materials.
Replace the old wooden floors with new tiles.
Repair and clean the chimney for safe use.
Clean and repair the swimming pool.
Install a new fence around the property.
Install a new security system including cameras and alarms.
